last_episode_to_air.overview: The six-part series concludes with a look at the lives of Prince William, Prince Harry and the future of the crown.

name: The Windsors: Inside the Royal Dynasty
original_name: The Windsors: Inside the Royal Dynasty
overview: From the producers of "The Kennedys," this six-part miniseries tells the incredible, dramatic and emotional tale of the British Royal Family known as The Windsors. Using stunning archive and interviews with insiders and experts, the series weaves together the true story of the Windsor dynasty.
